<div id="content" class="span12">
  <div class="hero-unit jumbotron">
    <h1>Welcome to Ultraviolet, powered by Blacklight</h1>
    
    <p class="lead">Ultraviolet is a front-end user interface for LucidWorks Search and Solr, developed by LucidWorks.</p>
    
    <p class="lead">Ultraviolet is based on project Blacklight, an open source discovery interface for Solr originally created by Erik Hatcher, Solr committer and LucidWorks cofounder. Blacklight is now a thriving open source project whose contributors and users include the University of Virginia, Stanford University, Johns Hopkins University, and WGBH.</p>
    
    <p class="lead"><strong>Select a collection below to get started!</strong></p>
  </div>
  
  <ul id="collections-list" class="nav nav-tabs nav-stacked">
    <% @collections.each do |collection| %>
      <li><%= link_to content_tag(:i, '', :class => 'icon-chevron-right') + collection.name, collection_path(collection.name), :class => 'btn-collection' %></li>
    <% end %>
  </ul>
</div>
